{"tid":1021352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲女子涉開車拖行男友前女友","createTime":"2019-02-14T07:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T08:13:06.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e32db0fe6955ebe1bb604ff0ec03387e8578e3","tid":1021352,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"(澳𨳊電台消息) 司警拘捕 1名25歲女子，她涉嫌開車拖行男友的前女友，受害者仍未脫離危險期。 事發於上週六 (3日) 凌晨。案情顯示，嫌疑人當時在停泊於氹仔盧廉若馬路的男友車上，等候男友返回寓所取東西，嫌疑人期間與受害人相遇，2人發生糾纏，有人爬到駕駛座開車，拖行女受害人約 2秒，女受害人頭部受創，目前仍在深切治療部留醫，未脫離危險期。 司警表示，女受害人與男友同居，分手後仍未遷出。相信案件並非交通意外，具故意情節，涉嫌觸犯嚴重傷害他人身體完整性罪 。 (鄺惠敏 黃偉鴻)"},{"pid":"9933262009701f836c36c9636149b3eeffc670b5","tid":1021352,"uid":20619,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"嚴重傷害他人身體完整性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2f4bfcdb5e05080495f6bfe9ba5eeed44ac6d8","tid":1021352,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"d乜鳩婆咁惡的"},{"pid":"d91f3287ab88b6eae4bd0eb01725440762009a55","tid":1021352,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"嚴重傷害他人身體完整<br />\n性罪"},{"pid":"43f31caaa028dbab00ede6d49698e574ed4ddf86","tid":1021352,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3LXSajHOx0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3LXSajHOx0w&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=b89daed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3LXSajHOx0w</a>"}]}